By Alex Olise
 
A secondary school pupil was on Monday crushed to death in Ogoloto Area of Ikorodu, Lagos State.

According to various reports, the incidents, which occurred around 7:30 am, led to rioting with angry pedestrian vandalising some of the buses.

Security agencies have been dispatched to the area to curtail the vandals.

Due to the unfortunate incident, BRT management has temporarily suspended their services, while the private operators plying the route have hiked their fares.
